Description: FreeSurfer cortical and subcortical brain atlases for the 'ggseg'
    ecosystem. Includes the Desikan-Killiany-Tourville cortical atlas (Klein &
    Tourville 2012), the Destrieux cortical atlas (Destrieux et al. 2010), and
    the HCP subcortical atlas with anterior/posterior hippocampus subdivisions.
    Provides unified 'ggseg_atlas' objects with 2D polygon geometry and 3D mesh
    or vertex data, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
